answers.body_markdown:
The type system is completely [erased](https://github.com/Microsoft/TypeScript/wiki/FAQ#what-is-type-erasure) when the compiler emits JavaScript.  There is no `T` at runtime.  Instead, you&#39;ll have to pass an actual string value to the `get()` method.

You can get some intelligent typing if you make a mapping from entity name as passed to `doRequest()` to the entity type.  For example:

    interface EntityMap {
        JobView: JobView;
        OtherEntity: OtherEntity;
        EtCetera: EtCetera;
    }

There don&#39;t need to be any objects of type `EntityMap` at runtime; it&#39;s just a helper type that the compiler uses to understand that the name e.g., `&quot;JobView&quot;` corresponds to the type `JobView`.  Mapping from names to types is something interfaces do well, so that&#39;s why we&#39;re using it.

---

Then, your `get()` method might look like this:

    public get&lt;K extends keyof EntityMap&gt;(entityName: K) {
        const response = super.doRequest(&quot;/api/fetch/&quot; + entityName + &quot;/123&quot;);
        return response as EntityMap[K];
    }

So you are passing in an `entityName` parameter of generic type `K` that must match `keyof EntityMap`... namely `&quot;JobView&quot;`, `&quot;OtherEntity&quot;`, or `&quot;EtCetera&quot;`.  So now at runtime, the value `entityName` can be used to call `doRequest()`.  Then the response will be returned as type `EntityMap[K]`, where we [look up](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/release-notes/typescript-2-1.html#keyof-and-lookup-types) the `K`-named property in `EntityMap`.  So you can use it like this:

    const r = new RequestyThing();
    const jv = r.get(&quot;JobView&quot;);
    // const jv: JobView

and you&#39;ll see that when you call `r.get(&quot;JobView&quot;)`, the compiler returns a value of type `JobView`.  

Hope that helps.  Good luck!

[Link to code](https://www.typescriptlang.org/play/index.html?ssl=36&amp;ssc=21&amp;pln=34&amp;pc=1#-IikcRbdY4ZwgMjAaBUFQAHgA0iDwchITAANbIQhsKwdO6rDYAPh4xOWhAAcjU6tA8RItopgGwKARoMoIOsBRB7ABeEQ4dZoAB07D+3B4ACIAPQbMjqqwqYCIdWq6AAahBtLZHJN0A1AEYAEwAZlVEgeShUamF+DFgvskBpLLW6wA2niALoPExmfmC+DC6DSiheaDKgGI6g8F30aNCkIAN3jwvl2N4qoOu08zoM6vV0Gzsbz+x2RyAA)

